name: differenceWith
signature: <A>(isEquivalent: (self: A, that: A) => boolean) => { (that: Chunk<A>): (self: Chunk<A>) => Chunk<A>; (self: Chunk<A>, that: Chunk<A>): Chunk<A>; }
description:
Creates a `Chunk` of values not included in the other given `Chunk` using the provided `isEquivalent` function.
The order and references of result values are determined by the first `Chunk`.
